# 🛡️ Quest Log — Gamified Goal Checker

### *Transform your daily tasks into heroic quests and long-term ambitions into epic achievements.*

Presented by **Team Contrails** ✈️

---

## 📖 The Scroll of Purpose

**Quest Log** is a gamified productivity sanctuary engineered to conquer procrastination and inspire consistent action. By blending RPG progression mechanics with psychological motivation principles, it transforms mundane habits and complex schedules into an engaging adventure. Users build habits, earn gold, unlock customizable rewards, and receive divine interventions from productivity deities.

---

## 🔥 Key Features

### 🎮 RPG Progression & HUD

* **Dynamic Leveling System:** Earn EXP by completing quests. Watch your **Rank Title** upgrade from a *Novice* onward as you grow.


* **Streak Tracking:** Keep the fire burning! Complete at least one quest daily to build your streak. Keep watch for **Streak Freezes** to shield your progress if life gets in the way.



### 📜 Quest Management

* **Single & Long-Term Quests:** Drop in rapid-fire daily tasks or design epic, multi-interval milestones with customizable check-in frequencies.


* **Intensity Curve Scaling:** Categorize your efforts (Low, Medium, High, Very High). Harder tasks scale dynamically to award higher EXP payouts.


* **Smart Filtering & Scheduling:** View your calendar in Month or Week mode, sort by deadline or subject tags, and manage items cleanly via modular grid cubes.



### ✨ Divine Blessings (Deity System)

Earn favor with custom deities based on your productivity styles:

* 🍈 **Melon (Deity of Consistency):** Blessed upon leveling up or closing standard milestones. Grants bonus Streak Freezes and completely shields streaks from breaking.


* 🚁 **Helikopter (Deity of Speed):** Blessed by obliterating long-term deadlines far ahead of schedule. Unleashes a massive **3x EXP Multiplier** on High and Very High intensity tasks.



### 🛒 The Economy & Rewards Shop

* **Level-Up Gold:** Leveling up infuses your wallet with Gold.


* **Custom Reward Creation:** Set up personal real-life rewards (e.g., "Watch 1 episode of Netflix") and assign a custom gold price to make leisure feel earned.



### 🎨 Sanctuary Customization & Themes

* **Automatic Theme Unlocks:** Premium preset themes (like *Violet Oasis* or *Gold Vault*) unlock seamlessly as you rank up.


* **Custom Canvas Mode:** Reaching **Level 10+** unlocks an organic color picker to personalize the entire app layout to your preferred color scheme.



