## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

A modern web browser supporting CSS variables, backdrop filters, and JavaScript ES6+.

### Quick Local Setup

1. Clone this repository to your local system:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/quest-log.git

```


2. Navigate to the project directory:
```bash
cd quest-log

```


3. Open the `index.html` file directly in any browser, or use a live server extension (e.g., VS Code Live Server).

